resentation","/images/presentation.png",[88,89,91],"h2",{"id":90},"about","💡 About",[93,94,95],"p",{},"For several years I've enjoyed tracking my expenses in proprietary mobile apps, but after getting into self-hosting, I wondered if there was an alternative that gives me the same functionality without\nlosing control over my data.",[93,97,98,99,109],{},"I came across ",[100,101,102],"strong",{},[103,104,108],"a",{"href":105,"rel":106},"https://github.com/firefly-iii/firefly-iii",[107],"nofollow","Firefly III"," and instantly fell in love with its features. Since it offers a REST API, I decided to build a web app that feels mobile-native. I also wanted to ensure it passed the \"\nWife Approval Certification\"—making the process as short as possible while still using tags and categories for those beautiful reports.",[93,111,112,113,117,118,121],{},"Several ",[114,115,116],"span",{},"bad"," ideas later, I've come to this version: ",[100,119,120],{},"A transaction assistant"," 🎩.",[93,123,124],{},[83,125],{"alt":34,"src":126,"style":127},"/video/assistant.gif","width: 300px",[129,130,132],"h3",{"id":131},"the-assistant-in-action","The Assistant in Action",[134,135,136,150],"table",{},[137,138,139],"thead",{},[140,141,142,147],"tr",{},[143,144,146],"th",{"align":145},"left","Action",[143,148,149],{"align":145},"Result",[151,152,153],"tbody",{},[140,154,155,166],{},[156,157,158,159,162,163,165],"td",{"align":145},"Write \"tag\" + \"amount\" ",[160,161],"br",{}," ",[160,164],{}," Ex. \"elctr 28\"",[156,167,168,169,171,172,174,175,177,178,162,180,182],{"align":145},"- Fuzzy search finds \"electricity,\" sets your tag, category and description, ",[160,170],{}," - Sets the date to \"now,\" ",[160,173],{}," - Sets Amount to 28",[160,176],{}," - Sets your default asset account.",[160,179],{},[160,181],{}," Just hit \"Save\"",[93,184,185],{},[103,186,187],{"href":35},"Assistant Tutorial",[88,189,191],{"id":190},"features","🚀 Features",[193,194,195,199,202,205,208,211,214,217,220],"ul",{},[196,197,198],"li",{},"✅ Beautiful clean minimalistic UI 🔥 subtle animations and dark-theme support 🌛",[196,200,201],{},"✅ Optimized for mobile, with PWA support for a native feel 📱",[196,203,204],{},"✅ The Assistant makes recording an expense feel like magic ✨",[196,206,207],{},"✅ Expand Firefly data with icons for all resources 🎨",[196,209,210],{},"✅ Expand Firefly \"tags\" with the option of subtags for better granularity",[196,212,213],{},"✅ Add \"templates\" to make auto-completing fields a breeze 📢",[196,215,216],{},"✅ Beautiful dashboard making it easy to keep an eye on everything that matters 📈",[196,218,219],{},"✅ Lots of tweaks and settings 🔧",[196,221,222],{},"✅ Free and open-source",{"title":224,"searchDepth":225,"depth":225,"links":226},"",2,[227,231],{"id":90,"depth":225,"text":91,"children":228},[229],{"id":131,"depth":230,"text":132},3,{"id":190,"depth":225,"text":191},"A delightful Firefly III companion web app for effortless transaction tracking.","md",null,{},true,{"title":5,"description":232},"L3N4sglc1tb9sOcm9dkQ1jjtgAGxxmNVGN5gaFXT-Gs",[234,240],{"title":16,"path":17,"stem":18,"description":241,"children":-1},"Learn how to install Firefly Pico using Docker or manually.",1774600208733]